  <!-- Task 2: Book Overview -->
  <h1>üìñ Book Overview: "Journey Through the Stars"</h1>

  <img src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61QqeBh5J-S._SL1500_.jpg" 
       alt="Book cover of Journey Through the Stars showing the Milky Way galaxy" width="400">

  <p>"Journey Through the Stars" is an exciting exploration of astronomy, cosmic mysteries, and humanity's quest to understand the universe. The book combines science, history, and futuristic ideas in a compelling narrative.</p>

